Clone a Dialog or Dialog Step
Cloning a dialog is a quick way to build your bot. Dialog step cloning helps you set up similar dialog steps with fewer clicks.

REQUIRED EDITIONS AND USER PERMISSIONS
Einstein Bots is available in Salesforce Classic and Lightning Experience.

USER PERMISSIONS NEEDED
To build and manage Einstein Bots: Customize Application, Modify Metadata, or Manage Bots

To clone a dialog:
Navigate to the Dialog tab in the Bot Builder and find the dialog to clone. Click the dropdown next to the dialog.
Select Clone Dialog in the dropdown.
Enter a new dialog name and API name.

To clone a dialog step, hover over the icon in the dialog step and click to clone. The cloned dialog step appears below the original dialog step.
